00:11:29,271 --> 00:11:32,191
- Maaf soal semalam.
- Tak apa. Kita tonton filmnya.

231
00:11:32,274 --> 00:11:33,150
Selamat datang!

232
00:11:33,234 --> 00:11:36,529
Di Kepentingan Konsolidasi Whitewhale,
